        "evidence": "<p>Addition of assigned points.</p>",
        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation:</strong></p>\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Score</th>\n<th>Thyroid Storm</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&lt;25</td>\n<td>Unlikely to represent thyroid storm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>25-44</td>\n<td>Suggestive of impending thyroid storm</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&ge;45</td>\n<td>Highly suggestive of thyroid storm</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>",
